title: BRIGHT CORNER UNIT IN PARAISO BAY!!
posting_body: ['Live like in Heaven!', 'Bright and Beautiful Corner unit with Wrap Around Balcony.', 'floor to ceiling Impact windows.', 'Spectacular sunsets and views to the water and the city .', 'Ceramic floors, dressed Closets and high end window treatments.', 'Washer and Dryer in unit and Amazing first class Amenities .', 'Roof top Pool , Tennis and Basket Ball courts, Billiard and Movie room', ', Children play room , Gym and Spa and much more.', '10 min from Miami Beach, 5 min to Wynwood , Midtown and Design District and the Arts District.', 'Easy access to several high ways .', 'The Revive Biscayne-Edge Water is in the Center of Everything', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
